# Name Registration

## Objectives
Create an application to add, edit and remove names from a array list.

## To exercise some concepts as:
* [HTML5](https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/)
  * Basic elementes (head, body), inputs,buttons, div, link etc...
  *  Attributes (id, class, type, value) 
* [CSS3](https://www.w3.org/TR/css3-roadmap/)
  * CSS manipulatio
 [JavaScript 'Vanilla'](https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/9.0/index.html)
  * DOM handling
  * QuerySelector document method usage
  * Event listener,
  * Function, Arrow function 
  * Array list methods
  * Template literals

## Features Required
* User write a name in text input and pressing 'enter' key to add a name to the list
* User can click in name on the list for edit of value
* User can click a button to remove a previously name added
* Prevent page reload on submit
* After the user press 'enter' key, the text input need be cleaned
* The names on the list need be clickable
* When user selected a name in the list, it need be loaded into the text are box for edit name